| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4530 — Recovery Inhibition (blackshrantac)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 975095f4-c263-5091-9e40-dca2278987ab"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
